OL,5, The Metropolitan Police is "assessing" 
OL,6, a report of hate speech made against MP
OL,7, Lee Anderson after he accused London   
OL,8, mayor Sadiq Khan of being controlled by
OL,9, Islamists.                             
OL,11,FThe force said it had received the     
OL,12,Freport after the MP claimed "Islamists"
OL,13,Fhad "got control" of Mr Khan and he had
OL,14,F"given away our capital" to extremists.
OL,16,FThe Ashfield MP refused to apologise   
OL,17,Fand was suspended from the Tory party. 
OL,19,FThe prime minister's official spokesman
OL,20,Fsaid the language used was "wrong".    
